This brand is a member of the Sustainable Apparel Coalition.

Breathable mesh and thin synthetic upper materials.

Seamless construction helps reduce the likelihood of irritation.
Discrete eyelets helps disburse lace tension.
Heel Clutching System(TM) is made up of an exoskeletal heel counter that promotes an improved fit and increased support.
Breathable fabric lining offers a great in-shoe feel.
ComforDry(TM) X-40 sockliner provides antimicrobial properties for a drier, healthier environment.

Gender-specific design features a lower-density top midsole layer that allows female athletes higher midsole compression.
Discrete Heel Unit technology enhances the I.G.S system by creating the ultimate in shock attenuation and stability.
AHAR(R) is strategically placed throughout high-wear areas of the outsole.
Propulsion Trusstic(R) mimics connective tissues in the foot by creating tension as the foot enters the propulsion phase.
Guidance Line(R) technology employs a vertical flex groove that decouples the tooling along the line of progression for maximum stride efficiency.

Your stride and style are on point when you hit the gym in the ASICS(R) GEL-Kinsei(R) 6 running shoe!
This brand is a member of the Sustainable Apparel Coalition.

Breathable mesh and thin synthetic upper materials.

Seamless construction helps reduce the likelihood of irritation.
Discrete eyelets helps disburse lace tension.
Heel Clutching System(TM) is made up of an exoskeletal heel counter that promotes an improved fit and increased support.
Breathable fabric lining offers a great in-shoe feel.
ComforDry(TM) X-40 sockliner provides antimicrobial properties for a drier, healthier environment.
I.G.S(R) enhances the foot's natural gait from heel strike through toe-off.

Rearfoot and forefoot Gel(R) cushioning attenuates impacting shock and allows the foot to move fluidly throughout the gait cycle.
Gender-specific design features a lower-density top midsole layer that allows female athletes higher midsole compression.
Discrete Heel Unit technology enhances the I.G.S system by creating the ultimate in shock attenuation and stability.
AHAR(R) is strategically placed throughout high-wear areas of the outsole.
Propulsion Trusstic(R) mimics connective tissues in the foot by creating tension as the foot enters the propulsion phase.
Guidance Line(R) technology employs a vertical flex groove that decouples the tooling along the line of progression for maximum stride efficiency.
